picked up weight since.

31:45.991 --> 31:51.910
Well, actually I grabbed these
from Mindy's Twitter page and--

31:53.041 --> 31:54.825
it appears
over the last three years,

31:54.869 --> 31:56.523
Mindy'’s changed very little.

31:58.046 --> 32:00.527
Would you please try this on?

32:03.443 --> 32:06.837
Mother simply had
a change of heart. Nothing more.

32:07.316 --> 32:09.840
Perhaps you'd like
to see some other photos

32:09.884 --> 32:11.930
my associate found.

32:13.192 --> 32:17.022
These were taken three months
before Grandmother died,

32:17.065 --> 32:19.676
which happens to coincide
with the changes

32:19.720 --> 32:21.548
made to the will,

32:21.591 --> 32:23.942
that was electronically signed.

32:24.681 --> 32:26.553
How could you hurt grandmother?

32:26.596 --> 32:28.947
Utter nonsense. I would never--

32:29.643 --> 32:31.166
You cannot prove any of this.

32:32.994 --> 32:34.300
You're right.

32:34.343 --> 32:37.303
Elder abuse is incredibly
difficult to prove.

32:37.346 --> 32:39.044
Which is why I called

32:39.087 --> 32:41.263
Deputy District Attorney
Mark Callan.

32:50.272 --> 32:52.144
Keep the damn ring.

32:58.628 --> 33:00.326
I'm really sorry, Ada.

33:01.109 --> 33:03.155
It'’s okay.
I know it wasn't you, Min.

33:07.420 --> 33:08.551
Thank you so much.

33:09.900 --> 33:12.120
I'm going to be
singing your praises to Andre.

33:16.255 --> 33:18.170
Callan,
What are you doing here?

33:19.432 --> 33:21.216
Did you just use me?

33:22.087 --> 33:23.523
Don't know what you mean.

33:27.048 --> 33:28.615
What if I don't take it?

33:28.658 --> 33:30.530
If Judge Carmichael
rules against us

33:30.573 --> 33:34.055
at the evidentiary hearing, you
go back to prison indefinitely.

33:34.099 --> 33:35.970
- Do we have a chance?
- Yes.

33:36.014 --> 33:37.580
We are very
close to finding Joe.

33:37.624 --> 33:39.147
And if Julia doesn't show,

33:39.191 --> 33:41.584
then Judge Carmichael
will issue an arrest warrant.

33:41.628 --> 33:43.064
You talked to Julia?

33:43.108 --> 33:44.848
I had to, Randall.

33:44.892 --> 33:46.372
Is she gonna help me?

33:46.415 --> 33:47.764
I don't know.

33:52.552 --> 33:55.685
Twenty years later,
she's still breaking my heart.

33:58.297 --> 34:00.125
I know this is a hard decision.

34:05.130 --> 34:06.348
What would you do?

34:20.797 --> 34:23.670
I've made my decision.
Accept the offer.

34:28.762 --> 34:30.155
Ms. Lopez.

34:32.200 --> 34:33.941
- Is that it?
- Yes.

34:36.726 --> 34:38.206
You don't have to take the plea.

34:38.250 --> 34:40.339
- Is it Julia? She here?
- No. Randall--

34:40.382 --> 34:43.777
All rise.
Court is now in session.

34:47.737 --> 34:49.261
You may be seated.

34:50.000 --> 34:52.655
I was informed
the People made an offer.

34:52.699 --> 34:54.179
- Yes, Your Honor--
- Uh, Your Honor,

34:54.222 --> 34:58.052
Mr. Mack respectfully rejects
the People's offer.

34:58.096 --> 35:00.228
The defense has located
Joe Loffton, Your Honor.

35:00.272 --> 35:02.274
And has his sworn statement
that it was Damien Owens

35:02.317 --> 35:05.364
who committed the murder
my client was convicted of.

35:05.407 --> 35:08.280
Your Honor, we spent
the last week discussing

35:08.323 --> 35:11.761
how a signed document
isn't admissible evidence.

35:11.805 --> 35:13.285
The court can't just admit

35:13.328 --> 35:15.156
a signed piece
of paper for the truth.

35:15.200 --> 35:18.028
Except in very
limited circumstances.

35:18.246 --> 35:21.771
Thank you. Ms. Lopez,
why did it take Mr. Loffton

35:21.815 --> 35:23.382
twenty years to come forward?

35:23.773 --> 35:27.212
Fear, Your Honor. Damien Owens
threatened Joe'’s family.

35:27.255 --> 35:29.214
Joe just found out
about Damien's death

35:29.257 --> 35:31.346
