37:05.310 --> 37:07.312
Randall, you're not
going to be alone in this. Okay?

37:07.355 --> 37:10.140
Talisha and I will be
there every step of the way.

37:10.184 --> 37:12.273
I'm going to set
meetings for you,

37:12.317 --> 37:14.275
