the reaction I was expecting.

38:23.910 --> 38:26.042
Well, our system of justice
can only be reinforced

38:26.086 --> 38:27.348
by thoughtful debate.

38:27.392 --> 38:30.612
You and I may
not always agree,

38:30.656 --> 38:34.050
but we must be assured that as
long as you wear that robe,

38:34.616 --> 38:36.488
you will always have my respect.

38:38.054 --> 38:39.926
Thank you, Judge Marshall.

38:49.849 --> 38:52.242
Hey, it's the goose.

38:52.286 --> 38:55.420
Goo, goo. Goo, goo.

